titles.title: It's no longer I that liveth

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
It's no longer I that liveth
But Christ who lives in me
It's no longer I that liveth
But Christ who lives in me

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
He lives - He lives
Jesus is alive in me
